{"tid":263110,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"老母發動技能有無巴絲想領養貓","createTime":"2017-05-29T17:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T15:11:13.000Z","uid":632,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9e98e6049a2afbd7ec6503434c3df36ca5311c4","tid":263110,"uid":632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T17:35:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的我老母趁我去旅行執到隻貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （好似係隻貓跟佢返屋企）<br />\n但因為本身屋企有一隻成貓<br />\n點知兩隻貓唔夾成日趁屋企無人就打交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身老母話放去SPCA <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢解釋左好多次都唔明 去SPCA姐係送死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我覺得都係一種緣份<br />\n佢咁痴人應該比佢係出面fing多兩fing比壞人／貓異工捉左咁點<br />\n仲旅行緊UP唔到相住<br />\n但有意可以tg先 比相<br />\n<br />\n貓女 未夠一歲但體型唔係bb size <br />\n身體一切乾淨良好 杜左蟲同虱<br />\n好乖唔嘈唔煩 易上手 但應該夾唔到其他成貓架啦<br />\n<br />\n淨係想佢有巴絲裝下窗網比飽飯佢食<br />\n佢話等我返香港搞<br />\n所以開post問下有無巴絲想要先<br />\n有意TG 睇相傾傾<br />\njackyson133"},{"pid":"266e729ddbf91457b058a08ef4a40106600b7025","tid":263110,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T17:37:58.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想養但屋企唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab9291a557dd10a768c6cbc46a0637a8ebc6273","tid":263110,"uid":116711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T17:39:10.000Z","msg":"薑九公釣雞"},{"pid":"1c8a07d9ca1b27220f7e0c32cf11f226d0133ce7","tid":263110,"uid":17352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T17:39:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1c8e413e9c2b5db9a8146ff7579a5ebd4d461e2d","tid":263110,"uid":87582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T17:42:01.000Z","msg":"有興趣呀"},{"pid":"2ada54f3fe38ed0c2ddbccc17730a8a2f26510d4","tid":263110